Research shows that the manufacturing industry has become the focus of attention of major countries around the world-Xinhuanet
Hefei, Sept. 27 (Xinhua) -- A few days ago, the national intellectual property operation public service platform released the "Global Manufacturing Innovation Index White Paper" in Hefei, Anhui Province.
According to the white paper, the manufacturing industry has become the focus of attention of major countries around the world.
This is what the reporter learned at the "2019 World Manufacturing Conference Intellectual Property Operation and Protection Forum" held in Hefei.
The forum focused on the upgrading of intellectual property rights in China, comprehensively explored the innovative measures for the operation and protection of intellectual property rights in the manufacturing field from the macro level of policy interpretation and the micro perspective of enterprise practice, in-depth discussion of hot topics of intellectual property protection in the manufacturing industry, continued to improve the ability of high-quality use of intellectual property rights, and accelerated the construction of intelligent upgrading advantages in the manufacturing industry.
The forum invited scholars from the State Intellectual Property Office, the Chinese Academy of Sciences, relevant domestic and foreign industry organizations, and experts from professional research institutions to share their experiences and offer suggestions on how to strengthen the protection of intellectual property rights and promote the use of intellectual property rights.
At the forum, the Anhui Provincial Administration for Market Regulation released the report "Analysis and Evaluation of the Quality of Innovation and Development in Anhui Province for Patent Navigation", according to the calculation results of the regional innovation and high-quality development index of patent navigation, Anhui Province's 2018 patent navigation regional innovation and high-quality development index ranked eighth among the 31 provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities in the country, and the innovation factor agglomeration index ranked fourth in the country.
The forum was hosted by the Anhui Provincial People's Government and jointly organized by the Anhui Provincial Administration for Market Regulation, the National Intellectual Property Operation Public Service Platform and the China Intellectual Property Development Alliance.
