What are the most three points from a free throw?
On the 27th, Beijing time, the NBA Development League announced the trial implementation of new free throw rules, each free throw is only shot once, and the score is determined by the foul.
O'Neal is a NBA star with a low free-throw shooting percentage.
Under the new rules, two points are awarded for a two-point shooting foul, three points for a three-point shooting foul, and one point for a foul plus a free throw.
In the last two minutes of regular time and overtime, the previous penalty shooting rules will be followed.
