Trudeau's "personality collapsed", can he be successfully re-elected
The "big hole" that tripped Trudeau out of his heels this time was dug by Trudeau himself little by little.
Recently, Canadian media have exposed a number of old photos of the current Prime Minister Trudeau, in which Trudeau dresses himself as a black person.
This was considered a clear act of racial discrimination and immediately caused an uproar in Canada.
After the incident, Trudeau repeatedly apologized to the public.
Canadians, however, aren't buying it.
Trudeau shot himself in the foot.
As political commentator Riley and others have pointed out, since the rise of the "anti-blackface movement" in the United States, Trudeau and the Federal Liberal Party have been loudly accusing opposition parties or dissidents within their own party of "making big mistakes" in this regard, and have repeatedly threatened that "whoever makes this mistake should be expelled immediately".
To put it simply, the "big hole" that tripped Trudeau out of his heels this time was dug by Trudeau himself little by little.
Trudeau, the son of former Canadian Prime Minister Pierre Trudeau, is young and handsome, and there was a whirlwind of "political idols" when he first debuted.
Originally a "political amateur", after taking over as the leader of the Federal Liberal Party, he fought an unexpectedly beautiful battle in the 2015 Canadian federal legislative election - the Federal Liberal Party won a majority of seats in the Federal House of Commons and won the precious right to form a separate government.
At that time, Trudeau put forward many deafening political platforms and ideas, such as "ethnic and gender equality", "ecological and environmental protection", "economic revitalization", and emphasized the elimination of corruption and "unhealthy practices".
However, in the five years since he was in power, he has been anticlimactic in almost all of the above-mentioned aspects, "driving high and going low".
Aside from the issue of "ethnicity and gender equality", he has "paid lip service" to a series of Aboriginal issues that led to the removal of protest tents to the gates of Parliament Hill on the 150th anniversary of Canada's founding.
In terms of eradicating corruption, at the end of last year and the beginning of this year, Trudeau was involved in the boiling "Lavalin incident".
It was revealed that he had exerted pressure on the departments and officials responsible for the investigation and punishment of the major violation of favoritism and fraud in the case of the construction engineering company "Lan Wanling" in his hometown, asking the latter to "raise his noble hand".
Moreover, after the incident became serious, Trudeau became angry with the official who disclosed the fraud case - Wang Zhoudi, mentioned above, was the first to disclose the fraud case and directly handled the case at the time.
Although the case itself is still suspicious, its suspicion is difficult to clear.
Many observers have pointed out that the collapse of Trudeau's personality in the five years of his administration is mainly caused by his own "digging pits", and the biggest "pitfalls" are none other than "anticlimactic", "self-reaping the consequences", and "being lenient with oneself and strict with others".
Canada's most authoritative Angus-Raide poll data shows that since 2015, the number of respondents who support Trudeau has slipped from more than 60% to more than 30%, while the number of opponents has soared from less than 30% to more than 60%.
While the other opposition parties and their leaders have also performed poorly, even a significant number of voters who still vote for the Federal Liberal Party are now unimpressed by the figure of the Federal Chancellor and leader of the ruling party.
On October 21, the new Canadian federal legislative election is about to begin, can Trudeau repeat the drama that won five years ago?
The answer may be in one word: difficult.
Whether it is from the level of enterprise competition, consumer experience, or from the level of regional aviation integration and Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei development integration, it has far-reaching influence and positive significance.
On September 25, Beijing Daxing International Airport was officially opened.
The Beijing News reporter learned from the Beijing Municipal Development and Reform Commission that the capital airport has been in a state of super-saturated operation, and the opening of Daxing International Airport will enhance the service capacity of the capital air.
After Shanghai, Beijing has become the second city in China to have two airports in the same city, similar to Shanghai Hongqiao International Airport, which mainly serves domestic aviation affairs, and Pudong Airport, which mainly serves international shipping and aviation, and the capital airport and Daxing Airport will also provide more subdivided services in the future to serve the differentiated positioning of different domestic and international aviation businesses.
The opening of Daxing Airport, from the perspective of business development, is more of a positive impact on the capital airport.
In 2018, the passenger throughput of Capital Airport exceeded 100 million, ranking first in the country, but compared with the rapid growth of business demand, there is still a significant capacity gap, especially the demand for international routes.
In order to better serve the needs of domestic and foreign passengers for tourism and business trips, and to adapt to the development trend of Beijing's increasingly open and international city, Daxing International Airport is positioned as a large-scale international hub airport, and plans to meet the annual passenger throughput of 100 million person-times and cargo and mail throughput of 4 million tons in the future.
Therefore, the positioning of the two airports does not overlap, and they are aimed at different customer groups, and they also have enough market space.
From the perspective of economic accounts, the opening of Daxing International Airport will obviously form a win-win effect, alleviate the tight situation of Beijing's air capacity, accelerate the growth rate of passenger and cargo throughput, and create an incremental cake for the dual-core operation of Capital Airlines.
From the user's point of view, with the opening of Daxing International Airport, the future does not have to focus on the capital airport travel, but also can reduce a series of problems caused by the excessive concentration of routes, such as the extension of the transit guarantee time, the slower boarding speed of passengers, indirectly increase the time of aircraft and passengers in the airport, intensify the burden of airport operation, and reduce the burden of shipping at the capital airport, in fact, it also improves the travel experience of passengers.
According to the media's estimation of the time and cost of various transportation routes to large international airports, such as starting from the South Fifth Ring Road and taking the Beijing-Kaifeng Expressway directly on the Daxing Airport Expressway, you can get there in 50 minutes by car, the fuel money is about 40 yuan and the high-speed fee is 15 yuan; and the Daxing Airport Line of the rail transit subway is limited to 20 kilometers and 30 kilometers according to the distance, and the fare is divided into three grades: 10 yuan, 25 yuan, and 35 yuan; the public can also take the Beijing-Xiongxiong intercity, and it only takes more than 20 minutes from Beijing West Railway Station to Daxing Airport Station.
In general, citizens have a variety of transportation options to go to Daxing Airport, and the cost and time are also within a relatively reasonable range.
From the perspective of trend development: Daxing Airport is positioned as a Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei transportation hub, so it is a little far away from Beijing's urban area, but it strengthens the radiation to Hebei and Tianjin, facilitates more people to travel, and is of great significance to the economic development of Hebei and Tianjin.
In the future, passengers in Hebei and Tianjin will be able to enjoy more international air services provided by Daxing International Airport, which can be seen from the transportation planning of Daxing Airport.
In addition to the new airport line that directly connects Daxing Airport from downtown Beijing, there are also a number of expressways connecting Daxing Airport and the surrounding areas.
Just as passengers in cities such as Dongguan, Foshan and Qingyuan in Guangdong can go to Guangzhou Baiyun Airport through Guangzhou-Foshan, Guangzhou-Shenzhen and other expressways, residents in Langfang and Xiong'an New Area around Beijing will also benefit from Daxing Airport and obtain convenient and efficient aviation services.
It can be seen that the opening of Daxing International Airport is not just the addition of a few runways and a few aircraft, whether it is from the level of enterprise competition, consumer experience, or from the integration of regional aviation. The integration of Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei development has far-reaching impact and positive significance, which is not only related to the long-term layout and development of Beijing's shipping industry, but also provides diversified choices for the majority of residents in Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei, and promotes the further improvement of the service quality of Beijing's shipping industry, which is more conducive to promoting the integrated development process of Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei and stimulating the economic and trade development of the surrounding areas of Daxing Airport.
Therefore, for the opening of Daxing Airport, we should not only calculate the small account of the individual in the economy, but also calculate the big account of the overall development.
