This company is just one microcosm of today's cloud-enabled manufacturing transformation.
In 2018, the Ministry of Industry and Information Technology issued the "Implementation Guide for Promoting Enterprise Cloud Migration (2018-2020)", proposing that by 2020, efforts will be made to significantly improve the awareness and enthusiasm of enterprises to go to the cloud, and the proportion and application depth of cloud migration will be significantly improved.
