In addition to becoming a key technology to support industrial transformation and the development of the digital economy, the invisible and intangible "cloud" has also unconsciously changed urban management and social life.
At this year's Apsara Conference, the "City Brain", which has been unveiled for three consecutive years, is still attracting attention.
